### Business Type

This flow is ideal for real estate agencies looking to streamline property assignments, making it easier to match clients with agents based on their preferences.

### Template Type

It is designed for real estate teams focused on client matching, property assignment, and lead management. It automatically assigns properties to agents and creates follow-up tasks for agents.

### Use Case

This flow automates the process of assigning properties to clients based on criteria such as location and property type. It ensures clients are matched with the most suitable properties, and real estate agents are notified to follow up with clients.
